[USAGE]
1. Compile Echo Server And Client Program using below command.
   $ gmake

1. Execute Server Program
   $ ./server
   Checking port 5000

2. Execute Client Program or Using Telnet Command.
   $ ./client
   helloworld    <= input here.



[other] connect to 5000 port using telnet from another screen.
   $ telnet localhost 5000
   echo    <- input
   echo    <- output
